fields.name: Americano
fields.description: A shot of espresso diluted with hot water, giving it a similar strength to black coffee but with a smoother flavor.

fields.name: Sandwich
fields.description: Hearty Sandwich with Eggs and ham

fields.name: Espresso
fields.description: A strong, concentrated coffee brewed by forcing hot water through finely-ground coffee beans. It's the base for many coffee drinks.

fields.name: Cappuccino
fields.description: Made with equal parts of espresso, steamed milk, and milk foam, creating a rich and creamy texture with a strong coffee taste.

fields.name: Latte
fields.description: A smooth and creamy coffee made with one shot of espresso and a lot of steamed milk, topped with a small amount of foam.

fields.name: Mocha
fields.description: A mix of espresso, steamed milk, and chocolate syrup or cocoa powder, topped with whipped cream for a sweet and chocolatey flavor.

fields.name: Macchiato
fields.description: An espresso “stained” with a small amount of milk or milk foam, offering a bold coffee flavor with just a touch of creaminess.
